  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fire reached more than 500 homes in Argentina</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Some forests in Argentina, with their fauna and flora, have been burning for days or even months. Now, there is a new fire outbreak in the south of Argentina, in particular in the province of Chubut. This new fire has resulted not only in the destruction of flora and fauna but also in the material loss of homes and the disappearance of at least 15 people. Our national fire brigade is hardly working on the fires with minimal resources to help in this hard situation.</narrative>
  </description>
